<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[415, 211, 580, 247]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[245, 290, 750, 330]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[117, 345, 496, 380]]<|/det|>
where \(n\) is a positive integer and \(\binom{n}{r} = \frac{n!}{(n - r)!r!}\)  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[80, 410, 385, 427]]<|/det|>
Arithmetic series \(u_{n} = a + (n - 1)d\)  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[246, 433, 533, 463]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[80, 487, 335, 503]]<|/det|>

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[246, 508, 428, 576]]<|/det|>
